2. 

In this Order – 

the “1992 Act” means the Patents Act 1992; 

the “1996 Act” means the Trade Marks Act 1996; 

the “2000 Act” means the Copyright and Related Rights Act 2000; 

the “2001 Act” means the Industrial Designs Act 2001; 








