section 84 of the 1992 Act; 

the register of designs maintained by the Controller under 
section 30 of the 2001 Act; 

the register of trade marks maintained by the Controller 
under section 66 of the 1996 Act; 

the register of European trade marks maintained by the 
European Union Intellectual Property Office under Article 
111 of Council Regulation (EC) 2017/1001; 

the register of Community designs maintained by the 
European Union Intellectual Property Office under Article 
72 of Council Regulation (EC) No. 6/2002; 

the register of plant breeders’ rights maintained by the 
the Plant Varieties 
